name: Marginal society
description: This painting depicts the expression of those who live in difficult conditions and still feel happy, the world is not balanced (lame) those who are rich are more dominant and have privileges, 1 rich person represents thousands or maybe millions of human groups, the capitalists dominate, and the marginalized society. the lower classes) are helpless, this painting pours out from everything that seems to live in a narrow place and coincides with one another, they can still be happy in that condition, and remain grateful.
